<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">

<h1>About Me</h1>

<hr>

<div class="row">
   <div class="col-md-7">
    <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 300, alt:"Profile Image", class: 'profile-img' %>


    <div class="skills">
    <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
      <div class="skill">
        <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
        <div class="progress">
          <div
            class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
            role="progressbar"
            aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
            aria-valuemax="100"
            style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
          ></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>

   </div>
   <div class="col-md-5">
   <p>A self taught software engineer who is constantly seeking  
   opportunities to grow my skill set in pursuit of my passion for an ever growing Tech-field.
   </p>
   <p>A lover of books, God, adventure and a Worship Leader at Redeemed Gospel Church, Zimmerman.</p>
   <p>Currently a Tech Support Analyst at Kopo Kopo Inc.</p>

   <p>
  <button
    class="btn btn-primary"
    type="button"
    data-bs-toggle="collapse"
    data-bs-target="#jobHistory"
    aria-expanded="false"
    aria-controler="jobHistory"
  >
    Job History
  </button>

  <button
    class="btn btn-primary"
    type="button"
    data-bs-toggle="collapse"
    data-bs-target="#education"
    aria-expanded="false"
    aria-controler="education"
  >
    Education
  </button>
</p>

<p>
  <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
    <div class="card card-block">
    Tech Support Analyst at Kopo Kopo Inc.
    </div>
    <div class="card card-block">
    Customer  Experience Associate at Kopo Kopo Inc.
    </div>
    <div class="card card-block">
    DSR Admin  (Intern) at Kopo Kopo Inc.
    </div>
    <div class="card card-block">
    Direct Sales Representative  at Kopo Kopo Inc.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="collapse" id="education">
    <div class="card card-block">
     KCA University(Bcom Finance)
    </div>
    
  </div>
</p>
 </div>
</div>
